{"tid":2458538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指剷「刺針」兼裁40人唔算多 　有線邱達昌：未來多買中國節目減成本","createTime":"2021-03-23T13:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T14:19:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"493f705e1a38beea62cba56e2097ed24681b6030","tid":2458538,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bnWob7MSmmz7zlGKJ84pePBFtaQ=/802x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IQ5RVTEX75B6NNPZ4VG5P64TWM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbnWob7MSmmz7zlGKJ84pePBFtaQ%3D%2F802x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIQ5RVTEX75B6NNPZ4VG5P64TWM.png&h=fc435b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n有線寬頻（1097）下午舉行特別股東大會，表決通過由公司向大股東永升亞洲發行2億元本金的可換股債券。會後主席邱達昌見記者被問到集資後會否買新節目時，邱達昌表示公司「一向都有新節目，我哋個路線唔同，ViuTV就後生啲，TVB就乜都有，我哋好難做」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，會上有股東質疑，公司早前裁員節省的資源，根本無法抵銷收費電視用戶取消訂閱，以至坊間批評招致的損失。有份出席的小股東引述邱達昌指，當時整個新聞部對高層有很大誤解，指當時新聞部有差不多400個員工，裁員40人不算多，「TVB、NOW新聞部比我哋更少人」。<br />\n<br />\n「希望唔好再俾股東鬧」<br />\n小股東又引述邱達昌指，其對2017年入主至今，股價不斷向下走，每次開股東會都「心中有愧」，期望下次再見股東時，股價會回升，「唔好再俾股東鬧」。據了解，邱達昌在會上表示，日後會考慮減少購買日韓劇集，改買中國節目，以壓縮成本，另外未來會將辦公室面積縮減超過三分之一至十多萬呎。另有小股東表示，場內未有提供飲食，「冇嘢招呼」，故先行離開。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210323/DUEXUS6TP5D4FCIUG6CLPLV5EM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210323%2FDUEXUS6TP5D4FCIUG6CLPLV5EM%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97SfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=7c82a41e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210323%2FDUEXUS6TP5D4FCIUG6CLPLV5EM%2F&h=0a374cb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210323/DUEXUS6TP5D4FCIUG6CLPLV5EM/</a>"},{"pid":"dd47056e83e11cf350410731f05c2a0a946897e5","tid":2458538,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":1